Rhinox saw Anubis missle coming towards Key. His Chaingun blew up the 
Missle, before it made contact. Rhinox then looked at Key. "Damn I 
need to get her to a cr chamber." Rhinox looked up and saw Koga's 
Missle, but it was to late. There was only one chance. Rhinox jumped 
towards the missle.....

The missle exploded against Rhinox's right arm. His Chain Gun was 
destroyed in the explosin, as was his right arm. "Ahhhhhhhhh." Rhinox 
was now injured, without any wepon's. "Slag, just Slag." Rhinox
turned 
and ran to Key. He quickly grabed Key with his Left hand. He turned 
around with glee as he saw that a row of 3 autoguns have just came up 
behind Anubis. "He should be bust with that, I need to get to the CR 
chambers." Rhinox ran toward the ark with key in his left arm.
